{"article_id":"9Tr0crXozOUcgX67","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"That 's no surprise .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"All","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"you 'd have to do","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to verify that fact","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"is watch the rotating Google doodles throughout the year .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"They frequently feature social justice warriors , leftist causes celebres and random slaps at religion .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Or you could check its search results ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"which tend to favor leftist causes and politicians over conservative ones .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"But Google is n't just liberal ;","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"it 's leftist .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"It 's so leftist","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that its vice president of Diversity , Integrity & Governance , Danielle Brown , participated in a public scourging of an unnamed Google employee","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who had the temerity","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"to question the company 's odd focus on `` diversity '' hires .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"The employee penned a 10-page Jerry Maguire-style memo","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"outlining Google 's obsession with `` diversity '' and why its practices amount to illegal discrimination","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"-- and pointing out","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"that the lack of women in top positions reflects scientific differences between men and women on average , not discriminatory social policy .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"This intrepid soul openly signaled his opposition to sexism","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"but then pointed out","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that personality differences between men and women on average , as well as men 's higher drive for status , could lead to wage gaps at the company .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"That is absolutely correct","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"based on a tremendous amount of available social science data .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"In fact , it 's also true","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"while women on average may slightly outperform men on IQ tests ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"more men are found at the extremes of the bell curve","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"-- there are more men on the upper and lower ends of the spectrum .","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"That would lead to the hiring of more men at prestigious companies like Google","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"based on merit ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"not based on sexism .","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"according to Google itself ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"such wrongthink must be curbed .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"And so , Brown stated","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that the memo `` advanced incorrect assumptions about gender . ''","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Not controversial","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"-- incorrect .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"The facts ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"you see ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"must be made","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"to fit Google 's theory .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Furthermore ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"said Brown ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` I 'm not going to link to it here","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"as it 's not a viewpoint","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that I or this company endorses . ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"But there was good news .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"`` Diversity and inclusion are a fundamental part of our values and the culture","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"we continue to cultivate , ''","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Unfortunately , this philosophy of diversity before freedom or merit has run amok at many of America 's major companies .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"And it has an impact on product .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"YouTube has reportedly been restricting videos","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"it deems controversial or inappropriate ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"and disproportionately targeting comics like Steven Crowder and educators like Dennis Prager .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Facebook has taken steps in recent months","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to curb its own biases ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"but only after a blowup with conservatives","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"who were angry at its apparent attempts","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to crack down on non-leftists .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Twitter has banned or suspended conservatives for mysterious reasons","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that it has never applied to members of the left .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Google has a pair of leftist goggles on at all times .","depth":3},{"id":64,"text":"Its users should n't have blinders on about it .","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"Every search result should be scanned for algorithmic bias .","depth":3},{"id":66,"text":"After all , a company","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that will rip its own employee to shreds","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"for defending its hiring practices on the basis of science and data","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"will do anything","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"to defend its leftist politics .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":141,"left":133,"right":140,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":78,"right":132,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":0,"right":77,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":120,"right":131,"re